{"word":"Γερασηνός","slug":"Γερασηνός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Γερασηνός, ή, όν</el></b> [of Semitic <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ orig.\">orig.</a>] <b><i>from Gerasa,</i></b> modern Jerash, located <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ c.\">c.</a> 53 <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ km.\">km.</a> southeast of Lake Genessaret. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Γερασηνός\">Γερασηνός</a></el> <i>the Gerasene</i> <b><a href='B:470 8:28'>Mt 8:28</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Γαδαρηνός\">Γαδαρηνός</a></el>); <b><a href='B:480 5:1'>Mk 5:1</a>; <a href='B:490 8:26'>Lk 8:26</a>, <a href='B:490 8:37'>37</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:γένος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Γεργεσηνός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}